{"product_id":"chicken-wings","title":"Chicken Wings","description":"\u003cp\u003eChicken wings, prepared in our signature style with a dry rub and par-cooked to make cooking faster, easier, and tastier! \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAdd our meaty chicken wings to spice up your grill, with a selection of sauces available for basting, these chicken wings will have everyone around the table licking their fingers. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eWhat you get:\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e600g or 1kg of par-cooked chicken wings, vacuum packed to lock in the flavour.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eHow to cook: \u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eGrill\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply sauce generously with a basting brush. Place over hot fire or coals meat side down, turn and baste regularly until slightly charred. Drizzle remaining sauce over before serving. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eOven\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 200(C) degrees, place wings in a suitable oven dish and coat generously with sauce. Cook in oven for 20 minutes, remove and mix after 10 minutes to ensure even coating of sauce. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eAir Fryer\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eApply sauce lightly with a basting brush. Place in air fryer, turn and baste regularly until crispy. Drizzle remaining sauce over before serving. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"600g (Approx.)","offers":[{"title":"Signature Dry Rub \/ 600g","offer_id":42970474447077,"sku":"","price":4.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false},{"title":"Signature Dry Rub \/ 1kg","offer_id":42980047028453,"sku":"","price":9.0,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false},{"title":"Buffalo \/ 600g","offer_id":42963601293541,"sku":null,"price":5.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false},{"title":"Buffalo \/ 1kg","offer_id":42980047061221,"sku":"","price":10.0,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false},{"title":"Mango Habanero \/ 600g","offer_id":42963601326309,"sku":null,"price":5.95,"currency_